   Wanda dazzled in a black, cleavage-bearing bikini as she enjoyed a swim in Ibiza. The curvaceous star was accompanied by her young daughter and a friend as she waded into the water. Wanda wore her blonde hair in a messy bun and accessorised with some large sunglasses. Mauro and Wanda have been married since 2014 and share daughters Francesca Icardi Nara and Isabella Icardi.   